        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b><b>Investing in Student Achievement Act of 2017 or the ISA Act of 2017</b></b></p> <p>This bill provides for income-share agreements whereby a student agrees to pay a percentage of future income, for a specified period of time, in exchange for funds to pay for educational expenses.</p>      <p>]]></text>
      </summary>
